description: Try our easy to follow Double Choc Fudgey Raspberry Brownie recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Double Choc Fudgey Raspberry Brownie Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 95 g Nestle Bakers' Choice Dark Choc Bits
95 g Nestle Bakers' Choice White Choc Bits
1 tsp Queen Organic Vanilla Bean Paste

recipeInstructions.text: Fold through Nestle dark choc bits, Nestle white choc bits and raspberries with a spatula then spread the mixture into your prepared tin and bake for 25 minutes. Turn off oven but leave the brownie mixture in the oven for a further 5 minutes before taking out and cooling to room temperature.
